003Cp>Line 1, alpha at 70 mm; rho at 61 mm; theta at 46 mm. Line 2, ypsilon at 66 mm.\u003C/p>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line1\">Line 1\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"50\" atMost=\"55\">50-55\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line2\" to=\"line2\">Line 2\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"42\" atMost=\"50\">42-50\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line2\">Interlineation line 1 to 2\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"interlinear\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\"/>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                            \u003C/handNote>\n                        \u003C/handDesc>\n                    \u003C/physDesc>\n                    \u003Chistory>\n                        \u003Corigin>\n                            \u003CorigPlace>\u003Cregion>Sicilia\u003C/region>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"ancient\" ref=\"http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462283\">Lipara\u003C/placeName>\t\t\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"modern\" ref=\"http://sws.geonames.org/2524378\">Lipari\u003C/placeName>\n                            \t\u003Cgeo>38.48333, 14.93333\u003C/geo>\n\t\t\u003C/origPlace>\n                        \u003C/origin>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"found\" subtype=\"discovered\" when=\"1969\">Discovered in 1969 during the excavation of trench XXXI (episcopal property). It was reused as a cover of tomb 985\u003Cgeo>38.467130, 14.953871\u003C/geo>\u003C/prove